item.description:
Venez nous rejoindre pour une soirée décontractée ... dîner, si vous voulez .... discuter avec nous !



Come join us for a relaxed evening ... have dinner, if you wish ... talk with us!

We'll meet at the former location of the Dew Drop Inn, next to Simply Green and across from the *new* Dover Chamber of Commerce/Visitors Center. The location is slightly north of the downtown shops and 1.4 miles south of where we used to meet (Kar-Min, now called Thai Country). Please park on the street or in the Chamber of Commerce lot directly across the street.

P.S. Khaophum's does not have a liquor license, but we may bring our own beer or wine. Also, people are not obliged to order ... so please come even if you ate at home or prefer not to spend money!
item.how_to_find_us: Look for the red and white French Meetup sign on the table!
